[normal]so sits on NIEP legacy group for the Built Environment (Local Governments national lobbying body for construction) 
[normal]and represent
[normal]s
[normal] the UK in Europe 
[normal](through CEEPuk, UK public sector employers representative in Europe
[normal]) leading procurement and local enterprise cross sector dialogue.
